Package edu.virginia.lib.ld2solr.impl

Default implementations of ld2solr SPI.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CacheAssembler  
    DatasetCacheLoader
    A CacheLoader that loads RDF into a Jena Dataset.
    FilesystemPersister
    A RecordSink.RecordPersister that writes OutputRecords to a filesystem.
    IndexRun
    A Stage of workflow that creates index records as NamedFields units.
    JenaBackend
    We subclass GenericJenaBackend in order to expose the Jena Model inside it, because we wish to manipulate that model directly.
    JenaIndexingTransducer
    An IndexingTransducer that indexes from a JenaBackend Linked Data store using an LDPath transformation.
    JenaModelTriplesRetriever
    A TriplesRetriever that returns its retrieved triples in an in-memory Jena Model.
    LDPathIndexer
    An Indexer that produces JenaIndexingTransducers from a JenaBackend Linked Data store.
    SolrXMLOutputStage
    An OutputStage that produces records in Solr XML form.
